            <abstract xml:lang="en">
              <p>We place ourselves in the context of representing knowledge inside the cognitive model of a robot that needs to reason about its actions. We propose a new ontological transformation system able to model different levels of knowledge granularity. This model will allow to unfold the sequences of actions the robot performs for better scrutability.</p>
